## Nested Models

```python
from pydantic import BaseModel

class LogAttributes(BaseModel):
    """Log attributes."""
    status: str
    service: str | None = None
    environment: str | None = None

class LogEntry(BaseModel):
    """Log entry with nested attributes."""
    id: str
    message: str
